    <item>
      <title>印度将注入 180 亿美元现金以填补巨大的流动性缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行计划向国内金融系统注入近 180 亿美元，加大力度缓解现金短缺问题。印度现金短缺问题达到十多年来的最高水平，一些人认为这损害了亚洲第三大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:27:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉、宝马起诉欧盟 因中国产电动汽车遭关税打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/tesla-bmw-sue-eu-after-china-made-evs-are-hit-by-trade-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克旗下的特斯拉和宝马汽车公司已起诉欧盟执行机构，这是继中国汽车制造商起诉欧盟对进口至欧盟的电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税之后的又一举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/tesla-bmw-sue-eu-after-china-made-evs-are-hit-by-trade-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技风险助长避险买盘，美国债券收益率跌至今年最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-yields-slide-to-three-week-low-as-tech-risk-fuels-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在科技公司导致股市暴跌之后，投资者纷纷涌向安全的美国政府债券，导致美国国债价格周一上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-yields-slide-to-three-week-low-as-tech-risk-fuels-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:34:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
